overview:
Jenelle is currently the Library Technologist for the Cadwalader, Wickersham & Taft LLP in New York City. She was previously the Technology Associate at the American Australian Association and the Client Support Librarian at the Victorian Parliamentary Library in Melbourne, Australia. She has had a presence on the World Wide Web since 1996.

She holds a Bachelor of Business in Information Management and a Master of Business (Information Technology) from RMIT University.
